# Build artifacts in cross-ecosystem benchmark fixtures —
# regenerated on demand by each ecosystem's tooling.
#   - obj/, bin/    → .NET (dotnet restore in integration test beforeAll)
#   - target/       → Rust (cargo build / cargo clippy in matrix — lint, Phase 10i.0.2)
#   - coverage.out  → Go (D021 runTests — go test -coverprofile)
#   - lcov.info     → Rust (D021 runTests — cargo llvm-cov)
test/fixtures/benchmarks/**/obj/
test/fixtures/benchmarks/**/bin/
test/fixtures/benchmarks/**/target/
test/fixtures/benchmarks/**/coverage.out
test/fixtures/benchmarks/**/lcov.info
